{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aa3a1bf937","title":"集中最大兵力彻底灭当面之敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"72683aff61","index":0,"year":1947,"month":1,"day":7,"articleId":"aa3a1bf937"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3a32189957","type":"paragraph","text":"集中最大兵力彻底灭当面之敌”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"aa3a1bf937"},{"id":"84a6120120","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年1月7日）陈、栗","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"aa3a1bf937"},{"id":"e381fe154b","type":"paragraph","text":"为着彻底弃灭七十七师、五十九师、五十一师，攻占邮、台、峰、枣，并相机灭二十师及五十二师残部，攻占临韩，将苏北之敌吸引至徐州以北之自的，如你们感觉现在手中兵力不够，请考慧从震林那里抽调主力一部北上参战，以便集中最大兵力彻底解央问题，而述阳则在不能保守时准备暂时放弃之","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"aa3a1bf937"},{"id":"681c37d09f","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"aa3a1bf937"},{"id":"9f7682b20d","type":"paragraph","text":"虞中[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给山东野战军司令员兼政治委员陈毅和华中野战军司令员要裕的电报[2]，指江苏却县。台、峰、枣，指山东台儿庄、译县（今峰城）和枣庄。[3]临，指临城，即今山东枣庄市城。韩，指韩庄，镇名，位于今山东微山县东南。[4]震林，即谭震林，当时任华中野战军政治委员，正率华中野战军第","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"aa3a1bf937"}],"page":{"id":"4ed0638def","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"aa3a1bf937","start":354,"end":354}}}},"__N_SSG":true}